        "type": "expression",
        "id": "203",
        "folderId": "195",
        "color": "#c74440",
        "latex": "k_{demo}=0.02",
        "hidden": true,
        "slider": {
          "hardMin": true,
          "hardMax": true,
          "min": "-1",
          "max": "1"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "id": "201",
        "folderId": "195",
        "text": "We want to find some scalar so that at x = X_{demo2}[1], we have this parabola equal exactly 1. \n\nWell, we can just plug in the x we want, and solve for the constant. "
      },
      {
        "type": "expression",
        "id": "202",
        "folderId": "195",
        "color": "#6042a6",
        "latex": "y=\\frac{\\left(x-X_{demo2}\\left[2\\right]\\right)\\left(x-X_{demo2}\\left[3\\right]\\right)}{\\left(X_{demo2}\\left[1\\right]-X_{demo2}\\left[2\\right]\\right)\\left(X_{demo2}\\left[1\\right]-X_{demo2}\\left[3\\right]\\right)}",
        "hidden": true,
        "lineWidth": "5"
      },
      {
        "type": "expression",
        "id": "197",
        "folderId": "195",
        "color": "#000000",
        "latex": "\\left[\\left(X_{demo2}\\left[1\\right],1\\right),\\ \\left(X_{demo2}\\left[2\\right],0\\right),\\ \\left(X_{demo2}\\left[3\\right],0\\right)\\right]",
        "hidden": true,
        "pointStyle": "OPEN",
        "pointSize": "15",
        "movablePointSize": "15"
      },
      {
        "type": "expression",
        "id": "204",
        "folderId": "195",
        "color": "#2d70b3"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "id": "206",
        "folderId": "195",
        "text": "Then, if our first X value is at some arbitrary Y value, we simply scale the parabola since it won't affect the zeros."
      },
      {
        "type": "expression",
        "id": "207",
        "folderId": "195",
        "color": "#6042a6",
        "latex": "Y_{demo2}\\ =\\ \\left[4,-2,3\\right]"
      },
      {
        "type": "expression",
        "id": "149",
        "folderId": "195",
        "color": "#6042a6",
        "latex": "y=Y_{demo2}\\left[1\\right]\\cdot\\frac{\\left(x-X_{demo2}\\left[2\\right]\\right)\\left(x-X_{demo2}\\left[3\\right]\\right)}{\\left(X_{demo2}\\left[1\\right]-X_{demo2}\\left[2\\right]\\right)\\left(X_{demo2}\\left[1\\right]-X_{demo2}\\left[3\\right]\\right)}",
        "hidden": true
      },
      {
        "type": "expression",
        "id": "209",
        "folderId": "195",
        "color": "#c74440"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "id": "211",
        "folderId": "195",
        "text": "We can then repeat this process, creating parabolas that have zeros everywhere except one target point, scaling appropriately"
      },
      {
        "type": "expression",
        "id": "212",
        "folderId": "195",
        "color": "#6042a6",
        "latex": "f_{demo1}\\left(x\\right)\\ =\\ Y_{demo2}\\left[1\\right]\\cdot\\frac{\\left(x-X_{demo2}\\left[2\\right]\\right)\\left(x-X_{demo2}\\left[3\\right]\\right)}{\\left(X_{demo2}\\left[1\\right]-X_{demo2}\\left[2\\right]\\right)\\left(X_{demo2}\\left[1\\right]-X_{demo2}\\left[3\\right]\\right)}",
        "hidden": true,
        "lineWidth": "5"
      },
      {
        "type": "expression",
        "id": "213",
        "folderId": "195",
        "color": "#6042a6",
        "latex": "f_{demo2}\\left(x\\right)\\ =\\ Y_{demo2}\\left[2\\right]\\cdot\\frac{\\left(x-X_{demo2}\\left[1\\right]\\right)\\left(x-X_{demo2}\\left[3\\right]\\right)}{\\left(X_{demo2}\\left[2\\right]-X_{demo2}\\left[1\\right]\\right)\\left(X_{demo2}\\left[2\\right]-X_{demo2}\\left[3\\right]\\right)}",
        "hidden": true
      },
      {
        "type": "expression",
        "id": "214",
        "folderId": "195",
        "color": "#6042a6",
        "latex": "f_{demo3}\\left(x\\right)\\ =\\ Y_{demo2}\\left[3\\right]\\cdot\\frac{\\left(x-X_{demo2}\\left[1\\right]\\right)\\left(x-X_{demo2}\\left[2\\right]\\right)}{\\left(X_{demo2}\\left[3\\right]-X_{demo2}\\left[1\\right]\\right)\\left(X_{demo2}\\left[3\\right]-X_{demo2}\\left[2\\right]\\right)}",
        "hidden": true
      },
      {
        "type": "expression",
        "id": "217",
        "folderId": "195",
        "color": "#6042a6",
        "latex": "\\left\\{\\operatorname{floor}\\left(s_{how}\\right)=1:f_{demo1}\\left(x\\right),\\operatorname{floor}\\left(s_{how}\\right)=2:f_{demo2}\\left(x\\right),\\ \\operatorname{floor}\\left(s_{how}\\right)=3:f_{demo3}\\left(x\\right)\\ \\right\\}",
        "hidden": true,
